title.en: Danna-sama ga Chicchai Mofumofu ni narimashita ~Watashi wo Akujo da to Gokai shiteita no ni, Subete Gibo no Uso da to Kizuita you desu~
Akugyaku Seijo desu ga, Aisuru Danna-sama no Oyaku ni Tachitai desu. (To wa Ie, Kirawarete Iru no desu ga)
Himegimi wa Wakaki Shougun ni Oboreru
Oshi ni Muchuu na Tensei Heroine desu ga, Mishiranu Momoiru Yurufuwa Ouji ni Dekiai Kouryakusareteimasu
Hameraremashita ga, Shiawase ni narimashita - Kizumono Reijou to Hidamari no Madoushi
Uchi no Outaishi Denka wa Kyou mo Gu Kawaii ~Konyaku Haki desu no? Mochiron Kyakkashimasu keredo, Riyuu wa Kiite Sashiagemasu wa~
Bad End Kakutei no Seiryaku Kekkon ni Tsukawareta Mob Hakushaku Reijou, Tensei Chishiki Mochi no Moto Kuzu Danna-sama to Kono Sekai wo Sukuimasu
Mofumofu Majuu to Heion ni Kurashitai no de Kowamote Koushaku no Kyuukon wa Okotowari desu
Watashi to Kekkon Shita Koto, Koukai Shiteimasen ka?
Doku-suki Reijou wa Kekkon ni Tadoritsukai
Kurokishi-sama kara Zenryoku de Dekiaisareteimasu ga, Sugomori Seijo wa Kyou mo Hikikomoritai!
Oukyuu wo Tsuihousareta Seijo desu ga, Jitsu wa Honmono no Akujo wa Imouto da to Kidzuite mo Mou Osoi - Watashi wa Kachi wo Mitomete Kureru Koushaku to Shiawase ni narimasu
Ane no Migawari de Konyaku shitara Naze ka Henkyou no Seijo to Yobareru you ni narimashita
